<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    ‚è∞ Organization Invitation Expired
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{recipientName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Your invitation to join <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong> has expired without being accepted.
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:20px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Organization:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{organizationName}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Invited As:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{role}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Expired On:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{expiryDate}}</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    If you'd still like to join this organization, please contact the administrator to request a new invitation.
</p>

{{#if contactEmail}}
<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Administrator contact: <a href="mailto:{{contactEmail}}">{{contactEmail}}</a>
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Best regards,<br/>
    The QShelter Team
</p>
